data.message: Implement PollinationsAdapter for Olootu: Created PollinationsAdapter in olootu/core/providers/pollinations.py. Features: async HTTP client with browser headers, rate limiting (15s between requests), progress simulation, proper error handling for 429/530 errors. Added to provider registry with init_default_providers(). Testing blocked by Pollinations API being temporarily unavailable (Cloudflare 530 error).
